{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":389666,"duration_api_ms":331637,"num_turns":39,"result":"Done. Here's what was done:\n\n**Problem:** The Milestone 2 commit refactored `lib/agent.sh` with FIFO-isolated invocation, activity timeout detection, and Windows process cleanup, but these changes had zero test coverage.\n\n**Solution:**\n1. **Created `tests/test_agent_fifo_invocation.sh`** — 9-phase test suite with 22 assertions using mock claude scripts to test the FIFO path end-to-end without requiring a real claude binary\n2. **Made `AGENT_ACTIVITY_POLL` configurable** in `lib/agent.sh` (line 193) — the read-loop poll interval was hardcoded to 30s, making activity timeout tests impractically slow. Now defaults to 30s but can be overridden for testing.\n\n**Test coverage added:**\n- FIFO path with successful mock claude (exit code, turns, null run detection)\n- Non-zero exit code propagation through FIFO\n- Activity timeout killing a hung agent\n- `_kill_agent_windows()` no-op on non-Windows\n- Windows detection variable state\n- `--kill-after` flag detection\n- Zero-turn null run detection\n- Metrics accumulation across multiple runs\n- FIFO cleanup verification\n\n**All 37 tests pass.** Shellcheck clean on `lib/agent.sh`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"6e9d6f8d-9839-407d-90df-a49405528950","total_cost_usd":1.6417229999999998,"usage":{"input_tokens":36,"cache_creation_input_tokens":61576,"cache_read_input_tokens":1651386,"output_tokens":17240,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":61576,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":36,"outputTokens":17240,"cacheReadInputTokens":1651386,"cacheCreationInputTokens":61576,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.6417229999999998,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast